cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use FEED, please cite it."
title: "FEED — Format for Enforced Evidence-based Digestion"
abstract: >-
  FEED is a self-bootstrapping, AI-to-AI document protocol that makes downstream
  LLMs ground their answers in cited evidence — and lets you mechanically verify
  that they did. It requires no install, plugin, or prior knowledge of FEED on
  either the authoring or the reading side.
type: software
authors:
